cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper focuses on using Convolutional Networks (ConvNets) for transfer learning and feature selection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of AdaBoost as a feature selection method also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed method, which could also fall under neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
